  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要画一个设备数据查询的流程图。核心场景是：API客户端发起请求，经过设备控制器，最终从数据源获取过滤后的数据。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "APIClient",
        "DeviceController",
        "DataSource"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白。我注意到API客户端和设备控制器都标注为Groupware_IssueTracker，这是同一个系统内的不同实例，还是您希望用IssueTracker来代表这两层？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "APIClient",
        "DeviceController"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "是同一个IssueTracker系统，但扮演不同角色。APIClient是入口，DeviceController是处理层。另外DeviceFilterInput要用Groupware_ChatRoom，DeviceDataFetcher用Groupware_WikiPage。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "APIClient",
        "DeviceController",
        "DeviceFilterInput",
        "DeviceDataFetcher"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我先画出主链路：APIClient发送过滤输入到DeviceController，然后DeviceController使用DeviceFilterInput。这里ChatRoom作为过滤条件的载体。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "APIClient",
        "DeviceController",
        "DeviceFilterInput"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "接下来需要DeviceController把实际的数据获取委托给DeviceDataFetcher，这是一个独立的获取模块。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "DeviceController",
        "DeviceDataFetcher"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "已添加委托关系。现在DeviceDataFetcher需要对接数据源，它要负责应用过滤条件。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "DeviceDataFetcher",
        "DataSource"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "对，DeviceDataFetcher向DataSource应用过滤器，DataSource也是Groupware_IssueTracker。获取完成后要把结果返回给DeviceController。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "DeviceDataFetcher",
        "DataSource",
        "DeviceController"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "完成数据流：DeviceDataFetcher应用过滤到DataSource，然后返回结果给DeviceController。最后DeviceController需要响应APIClient。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "DeviceDataFetcher",
        "DataSource",
        "DeviceController",
        "APIClient"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 9,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "整体结构对了。但我注意到DeviceFilterInput的标注是Groupware_ChatRoom，这个命名可能让人困惑——它其实是过滤输入的抽象，不是真的聊天室。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "DeviceFilterInput"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 10,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "理解，这是用ChatRoom作为过滤输入的数据结构或通道。那DeviceDataFetcher标注为Groupware_WikiPage也是类似的抽象用法？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "DeviceDataFetcher"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 11,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "是的，WikiPage代表知识库式的数据获取层。整个流程闭环了：APIClient发起，经过控制、过滤、获取、返回，最终响应回去。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "APIClient",
        "DeviceController",
        "DeviceFilterInput",
        "DeviceDataFetcher",
        "DataSource"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 12,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "确认最终流程：APIClient发送过滤输入→DeviceController使用ChatRoom过滤条件→委托WikiPage获取器→应用过滤到IssueTracker数据源→返回结果→响应APIClient。结构完整。",
